# Code Generation Rules

## Governed Generators
- freezed — immutable model classes
- json_serializable — JSON serialization
- riverpod_generator — typed providers
- go_router_builder — typed routes

## Rules
- Run `make gen` after changing models, providers, or routes
- NEVER manually edit *.g.dart, *.freezed.dart, or *.gr.dart
- Generated files ARE committed to version control
- CI verifies codegen is fresh via `scripts/codegen_verify.sh`

## Verification
Before committing: `make gen-check`
This runs build_runner and checks for uncommitted generated file changes.
